reviewText: It's just what I wanted. Thanks!
One of the best documentaries on the making of Jaws I've ever watched!

I have several of these bio. Inside Story specials... They are the best documentaries about film making available..... I own the Jaws one as well as Halloween and The Silence Of The Lambs... great interviews and insight to the film making process.
There is no photo on the package. It looks shady, like someone could have made it out of their own home after recording it on their DVR and transferring it to DVD.
